{
  "stem": "4361.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the story is-- as a matter of fact, I do remember what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a great deal of goings-on between the town across the river-- because Sighet was between two rivers, Tisza and Isza.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, across Tisza, it was Czechoslovakia, and there was a lot of contraband going on between Czechoslovakia and our town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The contraband consisted, I think, well, the Czechs at that time had very special-- were, I believe, woollens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the English woollens were much less expensive if you used-- you know, brought it in from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At any rate, the officers, the duty officers were bribed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they turned an eye.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They turned away and permitted the contraband to continue, except-- and this happened during my uncle's presidency as being the [NON-ENGLISH]-- somebody was caught very badly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in order to extricate him from jail or god knows what other terrible things-- which included really nothing more than jail for a couple of days-- the [NON-ENGLISH]-- I forgot now the word for [NON-ENGLISH] in English, not immigration authorities.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The, the custom authorities wanted an enormous amount of money from the Jewish community not to-- not to bring him to justice, this man who was caught with the contraband.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, my uncle, being a stern man and having principles, he said the following.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I am going to have the fine paid, but henceforth, no more contraband between Czechoslovakia and Sighet because it's illegal, and it's not right, and it's finished.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No more contraband.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, he was not reelected next year because while there was no contraband, business wasn't that good anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
